wikipedia_page.main: Hannah New (born 13 May 1984) is an English actress and model. She is known for her starring role on the television show Black Sails in which she plays Eleanor Guthrie, the owner of a saloon in Nassau, and also for her role as Rosalinda Fox in The Time in Between.

link_mentions.page: List of Disney's Sleeping Beauty characters
response: In Disney's live-action film Maleficent, Queen Leah - now under the name of Queen Leila  - was portrayed by Hannah New. She is the only daughter of the ruthless King Henry, King Stefan's predecessor. She remains loyal to her father by becoming Stefan's wife and later bearing his child. She would soon witness Maleficent, her husband's former friend whom he had betrayed, placing a curse on her daughter, Aurora. Shortly before Aurora's 16th birthday, Leila becomes gravelly ill and dies offscreen. Stefan shows no grief over her death as he has become paranoid and obsessed with killing Maleficent, but later notes his daughter's resemblance to her mother.

Edge of the World is an adventure drama film directed by Michael Haussman and starring Jonathan Rhys Meyers as the British soldier and adventurer James Brooke (1803–1868). The film also features Atiqah Hasiholan, Dominic Monaghan, Hannah New, and Josie Ho. The script was written by Rob Allyn, who also produced the film. Edge of the World is a co-production between Malaysia, China, the US and the UK.
